high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the stove top.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn around, go to the fridge across the room.
Cut the tomato in the fridge that is on the lower shelf. Close the fridge door.
Stay in front of the fridge.
Put the knife to the left of the tomato on the lower shelf in the fridge. Close the fridge door.
Stay in front of the fridge.
Take a slice of tomato from the fridge.
Turn around, bear left to the sink.
Wash the slice of tomato in the sink. Take the tomato from the sink.
Turn left, go back to the fridge.
Put the slice of tomato on the upper shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of tomato in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn left to the sink
Turn right to pick up the knife
Turn right then left, towards the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator door, then cut the tomato in the tray then close the door
Turn left and right to face the refrigerator
Open the door and put the knife in the tray and close the door
Face to the right then left
Open the door to get the sliced tomato.
Turn right and left, walk to the left then face the sink
Put the slice of tomato to the sink, turn the faucet on, turn it of when full
Pick up the tomato, face the left then right, walk then turn right towards the refrigerator, face to the right then left
Open the door and put it to the top tray
anns.task_desc: wash the sliced tomato, put it back to the refrigerator

high_descs: Move to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Cross the room and open the fridge.
Slice the tomato that is in the fridge.
Move to the other side of the fridge and put the knife in the fridge.
Move back to the other side of the fridge and take a slice of tomato.
Move across the room to the sink.
Put the tomato slice in the sink.
Pick up the tomato slice out of the sink.
Move across the room to the fridge.
Open the refrigerator door in front of you.
Put the tomato slice inside and close the door.
